name: SpartyCafe
0:
”Alexa, open Sparty Cafe”
”Alexa, ask Sparty Cafe to begin”
”Alexa, ask Sparty Cafe what is lunch today at Brody”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sparty cafe
des:
Allows you to find out what there is to eat on Michigan State's campus at any time of day. By simply asking it to begin, it'll prompt you for what meal you're going to eat. Then it'll ask which cafeteria you want to eat at. Finally which restaurant you want to eat at. It will then list off what is on that restaurants menu for that particular meal.

This skill is not endorsed by Michigan State University
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
